     "type": "html",
     "name": "question54",
     "width": "600px",
     "minWidth": "600px",
     "maxWidth": "600px",
     "html": "<h4 style=\"text-align:left\"><b><i>Who can you call if you have questions?</i></b></h4>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">This study has been explained to you and your questions have been answered. If you have other questions or research-related problems, you may reach Dr. Bandoli at 858-246-1733.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">You may call the Human Research Protections Program Office at 858-246-HRPP (858-246-4777) to inquire about your or your child’s rights as a research subject or to report research-related problems. </p>\n\n"
    },
