  {
   "name": "page26",
   "elements": [
    {
     "type": "html",
     "name": "question40",
     "maxWidth": "600px",
     "html": "<p><br /></p><h4 style=\"text-align:left\"><b>G. Optional research activity</b></h4><p></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">If the research I am agreeing to participate in has additional optional research activity such as the creation of a database, a tissue repository or other activities, as explained to me in the informed consent process, I understand I can choose to agree to have my information shared for those activities or not.</p>"
    },
