     "type": "html",
     "name": "question8",
     "maxWidth": "600px",
     "html": "<p><br /></p><h4 style=\"text-align:left\"><b>B. What Personal Health Information will be released?</b></h4><p></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left;color:black;font-size:16px\">If you give your permission and sign this form, you are allowing: <u>UC San Diego Health</u> to release the following medical records containing your Personal Health Information. Your Personal Health Information includes health information in your medical records, financial records and other information that can identify you.</p>"
